Would something like this work for you?

```    // Store the form element in a variable for easier access
    var myForm = document.getElementById('myForm');

    myForm.addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
      // Prevent form submission so we can delay it manually
      event.preventDefault();

      // Wait for 5 seconds (5000 milliseconds) before submitting the form
      setTimeout(function() {
        // Submit the form programmatically after the delay
        myForm.submit();
      }, 5000);
    });```
